{"data": [{"id": "4742968", "title": "Why Digital Storage Inflation Will Accelerate Seagate's Growth Beyond The Next 3 Years", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"TikTok and Facebook, YouTube application on screen Apple iPhone XR\" data-id=\"1200731050\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">5./15 WEST</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Seagate Technology Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/STX\" title=\"Seagate Technology Holdings plc\">STX</a></span>) is a company that has been punished by the market due to a 2023 slump in sales. I expect growth to pick up, backed by an increasing production of digital media assets that will increase</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1200731050/image_1200731050.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742968-why-digital-storage-inflation-will-accelerate-seagate-growth-beyond-next-3-years", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 13:01:40"}, {"id": "4742972", "title": "Dividend Growth Bi-Weekly Chat 11/09/2024", "description": "<p class=\"p p1 editors-note-first-article\"> </p> <p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a3bdf26f-7fff-e936-a8de-b0f31d6c095d\"></span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Welcome to the forum for Dividend Growth Investing discussion on Seeking Alpha. A new article is posted every two weeks as a space for sharing of ideas, discussing concepts, and digging deeper on DGI. All previous blogs are listed in chronological succession on the </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/dgi-chat?source=section%253Amain_content%257Cbutton%253Abody_link#hasComeFromMpArticle=false\"><span>main chat page</span></a><span>.</span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><span>As promised and with your valued feedback, we are publishing a new version of the article with some changes to make it more engaging. The structure of the article will now include a response from one of you in the community regarding your thoughts on DGI.</span><strong><span></span></strong></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><span>If you\u2019d like to share your DGI thoughts with us in future editions, you can email us at </span></strong><a href=\"mailto:moderation@seekingalpha.com\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong><span>moderation@seekingalpha.com</span></strong></a><strong><span> and let us know</span></strong><span>. We\u2019ll be looking at continuing to do this moving forward. </span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><span>For a reminder, you can find </span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/dgi-chat\"><span>our moderation guidelines for this space in our profile</span></a><span>. And please share your thoughts below to continue the discussion and learning on DGI.</span><span></span></p> <p><span></span></p> <p dir=\"ltr\"><span></span></p> <p><span></span></p> <p><strong>More on Dividend Growth Investing:</strong></p> <h2><span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742661-3-dividend-gems-you-didnt-know-could-build-lasting-wealth\">3 Dividend Gems You Didn't Know Could Build Lasting Wealth</a></span></h2> <blockquote class=\"quote\"><p><span>According to a recent <a href=\"https://www.cerulli.com/press-releases/cerulli-anticipates-124-trillion-in-wealth-will-transfer-through-2048\" rel=\"nofollow\">report</a> from Cerulli Associates, no less than $124 trillion will be transferred through 2048. That's equal to the gross domestic product of the entire world in 2023! $1 trillion in $1 bills would stretch close to 68,000 miles, according to <a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2009/04/08/What-Does-$1-Trillion-Look-Like.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">CNBC</a>. $124 times this would translate to 8.4 million miles \u2014 a distance spanning more than 330x the circumference of our home planet.</span></p></blockquote> <h2><span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742276-top-5-stress-free-high-yield-retirement-picks-for-2025\">Top 5 'Stress-Free' High Yield Retirement Picks For 2025</a></span></h2> <blockquote class=\"quote\"><p><span>When investing for retirement income, what matters the most is income sustainability and protection from inflation eroding the purchasing power. Once these basics are covered, the next aspect that comes into play is the required capital to achieve the objectives. The lower the amount, the better. Or we could put this differently - the higher income generated per one dollar deployed, the better.</span></p></blockquote> <h2><span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742955-tis-the-season-for-dividend-growth\">'Tis The Season For Dividend Growth</a></span></h2> <blockquote class=\"quote\"><p><span>With Quarter 4 of 2024 rapidly drawing to a close and the imminent arrival of Q1 2025 on the horizon, this season marks the most common time of the year for corporations to increase their dividend payout. This is done partly for financial reasons, so that the management team knows what to plan around in terms of return to shareholders for the upcoming year. As 2024 winds down, income investors need to consider how to position their portfolios for increased dividend payments in 2025.</span></p></blockquote> <h2><span><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742869-is-zim-integrated-a-buy-after-the-ex-dividend-date\">Is ZIM Integrated A Buy After The Ex-Dividend Date?</a></span></h2> <blockquote class=\"quote\"><p><span>We previously covered <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724982-zim-integrated-double-tailwinds-trigger-robust-near-term-dividend-prospects\">ZIM Integrated Shipping</a> (NYSE:NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZIM#hasComeFromMpArticle=false#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"ZIM Integrated Shipping Services Ltd.\">ZIM</a>) in October 2024, discussing why we had upgraded the stock to a speculative buy for dividend oriented investors, thanks to the promising market tailwinds and the projected expansion in its profitability. With the management already raising their FY2024 guidance, we might see H2'24 bring forth richer dividend payouts, thanks to the longer transit times due to the Red Sea disruptions and the ongoing dockworkers' strike in the US.</span></p></blockquote> <h2> </h2> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div><p><strong>Seeking Alpha's Disclosure</strong></p> <div><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a72babe5-7fff-2fa6-0263-0176e5ac280f\"> <span>Past performance does not guarantee future results. Content is provided for information purposes only and does not constitute investing advice. Any views or opinions expressed do not reflect those of Seeking Alpha as a whole. Seeking Alpha does not take account of your objectives or financial situation and does not offer any personalized investment </span><span>advice. Seeking Alpha is not a licensed securities dealer, broker or US investment adviser or investment bank.</span></span></div>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742972-dividend-growth-bi-weekly-chat-11092024", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 13:00:00"}, {"id": "4742966", "title": "Nvidia: More Expensive But Still Positioned For Strong Returns", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nvidia headquarters in Santa Clara, California, USA\" data-id=\"1547214730\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>Nvidia (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a></span>), one could argue, has been the single most important stock of the past few years, both in terms of dominating sentiment and driving returns at the index level. The numbers are pretty staggering, according to one </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1547214730/image_1547214730.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742966-nvidia-stock-more-expensive-but-still-positioned-for-strong-returns-reiterate-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 12:55:55"}, {"id": "4742960", "title": "Locking In Option 'Income' With AT&T", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AT&amp;T cell phone retail store. AT&amp;T is spinning off its media assets to concentrate on cell phone, mobility and high speed internet.\" data-id=\"1384839524\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Written by Nick Ackerman</em></p> <p>We had another rather successful option writing trade come to a close with AT&amp;T (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/T\" title=\"AT&amp;T Inc.\">T</a></span>) for the weekly December 6 expiration. What initially began as another round of short strangles on the name ended with</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1384839524/image_1384839524.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742960-locking-in-option-income-with-att", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 12:43:28"}, {"id": "4742959", "title": "With 60% Upside Potential, Okta Is A Key 2025 Cybersecurity Pick", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cyber Security Ransomware Email Phishing Encrypted Technology, Digital Information Protected Secured\" data-id=\"1420039900\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"827px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1420039900/image_1420039900.